+-----------------+-----------+------+
| table2_order    |         1 |    2 |
| table2_order    |         2 |    2 |
| table2_order    |         3 |    2 |
| table2_order    |         4 |    2 |
| table2_order    |         5 |    2 |
| ORDER==>ORDER   |         6 |    2 |
| ORDER==>ORDER   |         7 |    2 |
| ORDER==>ORDER   |         8 |    2 |
| ORDER==>ORDER   |         9 |    2 |
| ORDER==>NOORDER |   1000001 |    3 |
| ORDER==>NOORDER |   1000002 |    3 |
| ORDER==>NOORDER |   1000003 |    3 |
| ORDER==>NOORDER |   1000004 |    3 |
+-----------------+-----------+------+
